{"word":"H7158 - קִרְיַת סַנָּה - Qiryath Çannâh - keer-yath' san-naw' - Kirjath-sannah","slug":"H7158","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">קִרְיַת סַנָּה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Qiryath Çannâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>keer-yath' san-naw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Kirjath-sannah"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E7;&#x05E8;&#x05D9;&#x05EA; &#x05E1;&#x05E4;&#x05E8;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05E7;&#x05E8;&#x05D9;&#x05EA; &#x05E1;&#x05E0;&#x05BC;&#x05D4; - qiryath sanna&#x0302;h  qiryath se&#x0302;pher</b> - <i>keer-yath' san-naw', keer-yath' say'-fer</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H7151\">H7151</a> and a simpler feminine from the same as <a href=\"#/H5577\">H5577</a>, or (for the second form) <a href=\"#/H5612\">H5612</a>; <i>city of branches</i>, or <i>of a book</i>; <i>Kirjath Sannah</i> or <i>Kirjath Sepher</i>, a place in Palestine: - Kirjath-sannah, Kirjath-sepher."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4745\">H4745</a>, <a href=\"#/H4746\">H4746</a>, <a href=\"#/H6982\">H6982</a>, <a href=\"#/H704\">H704</a>, <a href=\"#/H7136\">H7136</a>, <a href=\"#/H7137\">H7137</a>, <a href=\"#/H7147\">H7147</a>, <a href=\"#/H7151\">H7151</a>, <a href=\"#/H7152\">H7152</a>, <a href=\"#/H7153\">H7153</a>, <a href=\"#/H7154\">H7154</a>, <a href=\"#/H7155\">H7155</a>, <a href=\"#/H7156\">H7156</a>, <a href=\"#/H7157\">H7157</a>, <a href=\"#/H7176\">H7176</a>, <a href=\"#/H7177\">H7177</a>, <a href=\"#/H7178\">H7178</a>"}]}